{"tid":2127496,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"曾鈺成現形？ - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-07-27T10:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T12:05:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7f86dea69ea84bebe057ecd8437f9b7d868031e0","tid":2127496,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:57:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200727/20963803/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200727%2F20963803%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpWmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=03fca420\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200727%2F20963803%2F&h=aed5950e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200727/20963803/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成現形？ - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200727/large/1595755563_08df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200727%2Flarge%2F1595755563_08df.jpg&h=f9070c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日曾鈺成在視像節目上帶風向，提議九月立法會選舉應該延期至少一年，他原話是這樣說的：「我認為政府應該當機立斷，現在就決定：將呢個換屆選舉推遲起碼一年。點解話起碼呢？我哋都唔知明年呢段時間點㗎。」沒有立法會的一年，曾鈺成表示行政長官可召開緊急會議，由已卸任的議員審議《財政預算案》等。<br />\n<br />\n很多網民看見曾鈺成這樣說，都指他「現形了」、「終於露出老狐狸尾巴」。我懷疑他們是否有點誤會。人家一路走來，始終粉紅，堂堂民建聯創黨主席，幾時隱過形呢？狐狸混入一群豬裏，只會更加顯眼。<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成唯一的存在價值，在其智力。有時候，他必須發表合乎邏輯、有理有據的意見，以證明自己的存在，博取部分公眾的信任。對於這類意見，<span class=\"orange\">如他指出「港區國安法」第五十五、五十六條顯然抵觸《基本法》</span>，大家就不該因人廢言，反而要活學活用&mdash;&mdash;「抗爭派」候選人回覆選舉主任問及是否支持國安法時，就可草船借箭，連消帶打，反問<span class=\"orange\">支持國安法怎可能同時擁護《基本法》。</span><br />\n<br />\n然而智力一旦赤化，狐狸大多數時候都會表現得像一頭豬，這不叫「現形」，而是叫。。。。。。。。。。。。。：你其實連聽日都唔知係點，何苦繼續做人呢？<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成這個建議，有三大不智之處。一、自揭底牌：讓對家。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n最大的不智是：你的選民年紀都不輕了，拖得太長，不怕他們越來越少嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com"},{"pid":"610667b0610f316069b4c770b7171a511c38ab8e","tid":2127496,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:37:29.000Z","msg":"唔好copy成段<br />\n放條link就算"},{"pid":"f96ac1f9fb4a06b71ce3b1c9b0b5e91c6f6e18a3","tid":2127496,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:05:23.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}